  "texts": [
    "This contributes to the nascent literature on using a PLM to identify causal relationships.",
    "2 We compare the characteristics of the map produced by our approach with maps created by individuals from the same large source documents (40+ pages).",
    "We use documents from two domains (obesity and suicide) and employ several individuals trained in systems thinking.",
    "As human maps vary, to derive distributions of their characteristics and position the GPT-solution with respect to these distributions.",
    "Our approach to evaluation goes beyond classic string-matching techniques and constitutes a hybrid between human evaluations (since they create maps) and automatic evaluations (which derive characteristics from maps)."
  ],
